Hotel.name: Park Inn by Radisson Cape Town Foreshore

Description.Text: Hotel has an Outdoor plunge pool, fitness centre, high-speed Internet access and indoor parking are all available at guests disposal. The hotel's state-of-the-art meeting facilities boast a business centre, pre-conference area and a 125 sqaure metres divisible conference room.

Guests can explore the city from this conveniently located hotel on the city's main artery, known as Foreshore, that connects Adderley Street and Heerengracht. The hotel's location in Cape Town city centre makes it only a two-minute walk from the Cape Town International Convention Centre (CTICC) and the Victoria & Alfred waterfront with its numerous dining and shopping options. The Cape Town International Airport is only 25 kilometres away, approximately 30 minutes by transfer. Numerous local corporate headquarters are located nearby the hotel, making the Park Inn a perfect choice for business travellers.
A large 120 room newly built modern hotel.

The Park Inn's RBG Bar & Grill serves delicious food and refreshing drinks in stylish and inviting surroundings in Cape Town Foreshore. The restaurant's tempting menu options and lively ambience are sure to make a stay at the hotel enjoyable. The versatile, all-day menu features signature items from the grill, including gourmet burgers, local specialities, soups, salads and light bites. After dinner, guests can relax with a drink at the RBG Bar, boasting an extensive South African wine collection, or make their way up to the hotel's rooftop bar at the pool terrace, boasting superb mountain views.
Hotel has a large lobby with modern decor.
